---
import DemoComponentCard from '../../../../components/DemoComponentCard.astro';
---

<p class='text-body-large'>A FAB represents the primary action on a screen. Use it for the most important action a user can take.</p>

<DemoComponentCard lang={'html'}>
  <wc-fab name='add'></wc-fab>
</DemoComponentCard>

<p class='text-body-large'>The extended FAB displays a text label alongside the icon by setting the <code>label</code> attribute.</p>

<DemoComponentCard lang={'html'}>
  <wc-fab name='add' label='Create'></wc-fab>
</DemoComponentCard>
